I want to reverse your course where you live and how you choose.

25:45.392 --> 25:49.477
I want to reverse your course this morning.

25:51.020 --> 25:52.722
And I want to do it for Christ's sake.

25:54.754 --> 26:05.430
Thank you for listening to this episode of Light and Truth, where we are committed to providing God-centered preaching to help you see Christ clearly and treasure Him truly.

26:06.091 --> 26:07.693
I'm your host, Dan Kruver.

26:08.815 --> 26:22.475
On our next episode, John Piper continues our eight-part series, Living and Dying for the Glory of Christ, with a message titled, To Die is Game, How Suffering Magnifies Christ.

26:23.197 --> 26:24.178
I hope you'll join us.

26:24.898 --> 26:28.466
For more resources, visit desiringgod.org.

